Safebait Dashboard Implementation Plan (Vanilla):
A premium-feeling phishing simulator dashboard built with pure HTML, CSS, and JS.
Proposed Changes
Core Pages
  index.html
    The main CEO Dashboard view containing the sidebar, summary cards, and charts area. Imports Chart.js via CDN.

  warning.html
    A professionally styled warning page that displays educational information to users who "clicked" the phishing link.

Styles
  css/style.css
    Contains global typography (Inter font), a sleek dark mode theme, CSS variables for colors, and fully responsive grid layouts for both pages.

Data & Logic
  js/mock-data.js
    Contains all mock employee targets (names, departments, status) and campaign statistics to power the dashboard visuals.

  js/dashboard.js
    Handles the Chart.js initialization (Pie Chart for click-through rates, Bar Chart for department vulnerabilities, 
Line chart for timeline), calculation of metrics from the mock data, and DOM updates.

Verification Plan
  Manual Verification
    Open index.html in the browser and verify premium CSS styling, responsive layout, and correct Chart.js rendering.
    Open warning.html and verify its educational impact and aesthetics.
